","body":"저기, 하나 물어봐도 될까?\nRoselia에서는 평소 어떤 반성회를 해?\n무척 궁금해.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event151-03-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"이거 봐!\n바로 활기를 띠잖아?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event151-03-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"루이","body":"딱히 활기가 도는 건 아니야.\n조금 참고하려고 했던 것뿐이야.\n우리도 반성회는 하지만 이야기가 딴 길로 세는 일이 많아서.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event151-03-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"반성회는 엄청 평범한 것 같아.\n연습하고 나서 신경 쓰이는 점을 서로 이야기해.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event151-03-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"음…… 라이브 끝나고 감자튀김 같은 걸 자주 주문하고……\n아, 뭔가 분한 일이 있을 때는\n다 같이 슈퍼 먹부림 세트 같은 걸 주문하기도 해!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event151-03-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":900000}],"windowDisplayName":"록・츄츄・마시로","body":"슈퍼 먹부림 세트?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":900000,"voiceId":"event151-03-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"W햄버그랑 새우튀김, 치킨소테 플레이트,\n밥 곱빼기에 디저트까지 나오는 세트야~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event151-03-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"마시로","body":"그, 그걸 다 먹을 수 있어?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"event151-03-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whe